wiki.summary: S-Class (특) is a song recorded by South Korean boy group Stray Kids. It is the second and title track from their third studio album ★★★★★ (5-STAR) released on June 2, 2023. The song is as fresh and challenging as Stray Kids can be, with a message of being the "weirdest of the weird and the brightest of the special." It features a catchy and unique rhythmic hook that jumps between different sound sources, song forms, and feels like a mashup of several songs all in one. (★★★★★ (5-STAR) Album Introduction) Read more on Last.fm.
